---
title: 'Blackened' Shrimp  with Pineapple Salsa and Black Bean Rice
description: Quick supper gets a zing of fun Cajun flavours with 'blackened' shrimp! Cooking tender shrimp at a high heat gives a dark and flavourful crust in no time.
